doctype html
html
    head
        title= 'MyTailer'
        link(rel='stylesheet', href='/stylesheets/bootstrap/css/bootstrap.min.css')
        meta(name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1")
        script(src='/javascripts/jquery-2.1.4.js')
        style.
            html{ 
                background: url(/images/cEntryBg3.jpg) no-repeat center center fixed; 
                -webkit-background-size: cover;
                -moz-background-size: cover;
                -o-background-size: cover;
                background-size: cover;
            }
            .alert{
                max-width: 70%;
                margin: 0px auto 10px auto;
            }
            .panel{
                max-width:600px;
                background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7);
            }
            body{
                background-size: contain;
            }
            .P-customerEntry{ 
                margin-left: 16%;
                margin-top: 10%;
                margin-bottom: 0px;
            }	   
            @media only screen  
                and (max-device-width: 736px) { 
                   .panel{
                        max-width: 80%;
                    }
                }
            .smooth-corner{
                border-radius: 10px 10px 10px 10px; 
                -moz-border-radius: 10px 10px 10px 10px;
                -webkit-border-radius: 10px 10px 10px 10px;
                border: 0px solid #000000;
            }
            .entryBtn{
                width: 50%;
                border-radius: 0;
            }
            .entryExp{
                width: 20%;
                color: #fff;
            }
            .entryTitle{
                color: rgba(255,223,0,0.95);
                font-weight: bold;
                font-size: 64px;
                margin-top: 30%;
            }
            .btn-primary {
                color: #fff;
                background-color: rgba(212,175,55,0.7);
                border-color: rgba(212,175,55,0.8);
            }
            .btn-primary:disabled {
                color: #fff;
                background-color: rgba(212,175,55,0.8);
                border-color: rgba(212,175,55,0.8);
            }
            .btn-primary:hover, .btn-primary:focus, .btn-primary:active, .btn-primary:disabled:hover, .btn-primary.active, .open>.dropdown-toggle.btn-primary{
                color: #fff;
                background-color: rgba(212,175,55,1);
                border-color: rgba(212,175,55,1);
            }
    body(style="background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0); text-align: center;")  
        div(class="3Btn-customerEntry" style="margin-top: 73%;")
            p(class="P-customerEntry")
                a(href="/myCustomer/chooseType" class="entryBtn btn btn-primary btn-lg " role="button") 逛裁缝铺
                button(type="button" class="entryExp btn btn-link" data-toggle="modal" data-target="#myModal1") 说明
            //Modal
            div(class="modal fade" id="myModal1" role="dialog")
                div(class="modal-dialog")
                //Modal content
                div(class="modal-content")
                    div(class="modal-header")
                        button(type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal")&times
                        h4(class="modal-title")裁缝铺
                    div(class="modal-body")
                        p   您可以从各式各样的裁缝铺中挑选您中意的款式，然后通过沟通，裁缝可以根据您的需求，做出最大限度的修改，定制出为您量身打造的服装
            p(class="P-customerEntry")
                button(class="entryBtn btn btn-primary btn-lg" disabled="disabled") 逛设计师店
                button(type="button" class="entryExp btn btn-link" data-toggle="modal" data-target="#myModal2") 说明
            div(class="modal fade" id="myModal2" role="dialog")
                div(class="modal-dialog")
                div(class="modal-content")
                    div(class="modal-header")
                        button(type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal")&times
                        h4(class="modal-title")设计师店（功能开发中）
                    div(class="modal-body")
                        p   您可以浏览到各个出色设计师晒出的特制款式服装，但是设计师款的服装可以接受的修改选项相对较少
            p(style="color: rgba(212,175,55,1); margin-bottom:0px;")
                即&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp将&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp推&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp出
            p(class="P-customerEntry" style="margin-top: 6%;")
                button(class="entryBtn btn btn-primary btn-lg" disabled="disabled") 我有设计图
                button(type="button" class="entryExp btn btn-link" data-toggle="modal" data-target="#myModal3") 说明
            div(class="modal fade" id="myModal3" role="dialog")
                div(class="modal-dialog")
                div(class="modal-content")
                    div(class="modal-header")
                        button(type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal")&times
                        h4(class="modal-title")我有设计图（功能开发中）
                    div(class="modal-body")
                        p   上传自己精心设计或者心怡的款式图片，我们将为您寻找出色的裁缝将其变为现实
            p(style="color: rgba(212,175,55,1);")
                即&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp将&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp推&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp出
        footer 
            script(src='/stylesheets/bootstrap/js/bootstrap.min.js')